<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Observable Collection Binding Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Essential Chart can be bound to an <Run FontWeight="Bold">Observable Collection</Run> instance, and changes regarding this collection (adding new items, deleting existing items, and updates in existing items) are automatically reflected by the chart during run-time.</Paragraph>

