<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>A chart can be bound to an Observable Collection instance.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Changes notified by this collection are automatically reflected by the chart during run-time.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Use the DataGrid to
                <Bold>Add/Edit</Bold> the records of the underbound Observable Collection source.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Click the
                <Bold>"Remove"</Bold> button to remove the selected value in the chart series.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
</List>
